Sentencas: The numerical model of a solid oxide fuel cell fuelled with methane via an internal reforming is presented in the paper.
Titulo: Performance of a tubular fuel cell with internal methane reforming

Sentencas: The model has been implemented into the commercial CFD code.
Titulo: Performance of a tubular fuel cell with internal methane reforming

Sentencas: The basic model for fuel cell fed with humidified hydrogen has been extended to cope with mixture of hydrogen, carbon monoxide and methane as a fuel.
Titulo: Performance of a tubular fuel cell with internal methane reforming

Sentencas: Numerical calculations have been performed to predict the tubular fuel cell performance for various current densities, electrochemical reaction rate ratio and steam-to-carbon ratio.
Titulo: Performance of a tubular fuel cell with internal methane reforming
